### 20. Get Orders by Customer Email - John Doe
GET {{CustomerOrder_HostAddress}}/api/orders/customer/john.doe@example.com
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### 21. Get Order by Order Number - Not Found
GET {{CustomerOrder_HostAddress}}/api/orders/ORD-99999999-999999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 22. Get Order by Order Number (Replace ORDER_NUMBER with actual order number from response above)
GET {{CustomerOrder_HostAddress}}/api/orders/ORD-20260407-AFCD3B
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 23. Get Orders by Customer Email - Jane Smith
GET {{CustomerOrder_HostAddress}}/api/orders/customer/jane.smith@example.com
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 24. Get Orders by Customer Email - Not Found
GET {{CustomerOrder_HostAddress}}/api/orders/customer/notfound@example.com
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


