### ========================================
### ORDER FILTERING & PAGINATION
### ========================================

### 32. Get All Orders - Default Pagination (Page 1, Size 10)
GET {{CustomerOrder_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 33. Get All Orders - Page 1, Size 5
GET {{CustomerOrder_HostAddress}}/api/orders?pageNumber=1&pageSize=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 34. Get All Orders - Page 2, Size 5
GET {{CustomerOrder_HostAddress}}/api/orders?pageNumber=2&pageSize=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 35. Filter Orders by Status - Pending
GET {{CustomerOrder_HostAddress}}/api/orders?status=Pending
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 36. Filter Orders by Status - Shipped
GET {{CustomerOrder_HostAddress}}/api/orders?status=Shipped
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 37. Filter Orders by Status - Delivered
GET {{CustomerOrder_HostAddress}}/api/orders?status=Delivered
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 38. Filter Orders by Status - Confirmed
GET {{CustomerOrder_HostAddress}}/api/orders?status=Confirmed
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 39. Filter Orders by Status - Cancelled
GET {{CustomerOrder_HostAddress}}/api/orders?status=Cancelled
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 40. Filter Orders by Date Range - April 2026
GET {{CustomerOrder_HostAddress}}/api/orders?startDate=2026-04-01&endDate=2026-04-30
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 41. Filter Orders by Date Range - Last 7 Days
GET {{CustomerOrder_HostAddress}}/api/orders?startDate=2026-03-31&endDate=2026-04-07
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 42. Filter Orders by Date and Status - April 2026, Shipped
GET {{CustomerOrder_HostAddress}}/api/orders?startDate=2026-04-01&endDate=2026-04-30&status=Shipped
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 43. Filter Orders - Complex Query (Date Range + Status + Pagination)
GET {{CustomerOrder_HostAddress}}/api/orders?startDate=2026-04-01&endDate=2026-04-30&status=Pending&pageNumber=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 44. Filter Orders - Invalid Page Number (Should return error or empty)
GET {{CustomerOrder_HostAddress}}/api/orders?pageNumber=0&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 45. Filter Orders - Exceed Max Page Size (Should use max allowed)
GET {{CustomerOrder_HostAddress}}/api/orders?pageNumber=1&pageSize=1000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
